      <title>避险情绪加剧船舶袭击事件，油价延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-24</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于更广泛的市场避险情绪抵消了也门船只袭击事件的升级，油价连续第二个交易日下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-24</guid>
